<plot>This tape features an interview with Peter Purves who played two roles in 'Doctor Who'. Morton Dill in 'The Chase' and more famously Steven Taylor who started as a companion in that story and stayed onboard the TARDIS until 'The Savages'. It also covers other aspects of Peter's career such as his long stint as a presenter on 'Blue Peter'.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?385648</url></doc>
